results.name: Expansion of Sum_{k>=1} x^(k^3) / (1 - x^(k^3))^2.
comment: Sum of divisors d of n such that n/d is a cube.
link: Antti Karttunen, Table of n, a(n) for n = 1..20000
formula: a(n) = Sum_{d|n} A010057(n/d) * d. Dirichlet convolution of A000027 and A010057.
mathematica: nmax = 75; CoefficientList[Series[Sum[x^(k^3)/(1 - x^(k^3))^2, {k, 1, Floor[nmax^(1/3)] + 1}], {x, 0, nmax}], x] // Rest
results.author: _Ilya Gutkovskiy_, Sep 19 2019
